                  I'm a data analyst with three years of experience. My day-to-day work includes designing indicator frameworks, quantitative modeling, attribution and anomaly analysis, and building BI dashboards in Tableau, PowerBI, and FineBI. I've delivered across e-commerce, smart manufacturing, finance, and education.
