                  data-en="Shanghai, CN  ·  Open to remote & collaboration"
                  data-zh="中国 上海  ·  接受远程 / 合作">
              Shanghai, CN  ·  Open to remote &amp; collaboration
            </span>
            <span class="text-ink2"
                  data-i18n
                  data-en="Mandarin · English"
